the public will believe them.

1595
01:17:57.835 --> 01:17:59.245
Performance and reporting

1596
01:17:59.245 --> 01:18:01.525
and accountability data seems to me like an iceberg.

1597
01:18:02.325 --> 01:18:04.595
Often just the tip is publicly accessible.

1598
01:18:05.015 --> 01:18:06.635
The far more important, relevant

1599
01:18:06.635 --> 01:18:08.835
and interesting information, the bulk

1600
01:18:08.835 --> 01:18:10.955
of information lies hidden beneath the surface.

1601
