Coast and HU Valley District.

1627
01:19:23.235 --> 01:19:26.255
The single report reveals for the first time ever

1628
01:19:26.845 --> 01:19:29.855
that deaths and adverse events have occurred due

1629
01:19:29.855 --> 01:19:30.895
to resource constraints.

1630
01:19:32.075 --> 01:19:33.425
Since the health reforms,

1631
