1634
01:19:41.145 --> 01:19:42.505
provided by Health New Zealand locally.

1635
01:19:44.345 --> 01:19:46.675
Some local accountability could have been achieved

1636
01:19:46.675 --> 01:19:49.355
through localities and iwi Maori partnership boards,

1637
01:19:49.375 --> 01:19:51.355
but localities have been discontinued

1638
01:19:51.735 --> 01:19:53.115
and the accountability role

1639
01:19:53.175 --> 01:19:55.155
of these boards has been weakened in the changes

1640
01:19:55.215 --> 01:19:57.075
